  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing Hope Through Chess</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At the Maximum Security Prison on Trinidad and Tobago, there are many inmates who committed crimes at an early age and are now paying for their mistakes decades later. These persons would have missed out on key opportunities to develop personally and professionally. Many are actually quite talented. This project will allow for approximately 300 inmates the opportunity to develop key skills e.g. decision making and critical thinking, that can assist in their transition back to normal life.</narrative>
  </description>
